EmberAI Features

AI Models
• Apple on-device AI (Mochi) — private, no data leaves the device
• Llama 70B (cloud) — expressive roleplay
• Qwen3 32B (cloud) — reasoning and creative writing
• Mixtral 8x7B (cloud) — lightweight and fast
• Switch models at any time within a conversation

Characters
• Pre-built roster of original characters across multiple genres (fantasy, mystery, romance, sci-fi, comedy, action, etc.)
• Each character has a unique personality, tone, expertise, catchphrase, and immersive opening scenario
• Characters respond with narration, inner thoughts, and dialogue
• Filter characters by tags, gender, and popularity
• Sort by Latest, Discover, Popular, or Recommended

Custom Character Creation
• Create your own AI characters
• Define name, personality, tone, backstory, and starting scenario
• Assign tags and gender
• Characters saved locally and accessible from your profile

Conversations
• Multiple concurrent conversations
• Custom instructions per chat (adjust character behavior)
• Supporting characters — add characters from recent chats into a conversation for multi-character scenes
• Chat history with recent chats view
• Rename conversations
• Start new chats at any time
• Clear all chat history from settings

Personalization
• Onboarding flow: name, age, gender, preferred content tags
• Characters address you by name
• Tag preferences influence character recommendations
• Editable display name from profile

Gem System (Virtual Currency)
• 200 gems to start
• 2 gems per message sent
• Daily bonus: 30 free gems
• Watch rewarded ads: 25 gems each, up to 5 per day
• In-app purchase gem packs

Settings & Preferences
• Toggle notifications
• Toggle haptic feedback
• NSFW character filter (age-gated, 18+)
• Clear all chat history

Privacy
• On-device AI option processes conversations entirely on the user's iPhone
• No account or login required
